WWW-Scraper-ISBN-WordPower_Driver
=================================

This module is a Perl extension for ISBN search collection that is provide by
WWW::Scraper::ISBN.

This driver searches for book information from the Word Power online catalog.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

  WWW::Scraper::ISBN
  WWW::Scraper::ISBN::Record
  WWW::Scraper::ISBN::Driver
  WWW::Mechanize

For testing the module requires these modules:

  Data::Dumper
  IO::File
  Test::More

For optional testing the module would like these other modules:

  Test::CPAN::Meta
  Test::CPAN::Meta::JSON
  Test::Pod
  Test::Pod::Coverage

